2026-05-11T07:05:41.6835789Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6836843Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6837940Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6838797Z 19        we only request it when the toggle is on.
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6839427Z 20    -->
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6840149Z 21    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT" />
