2026-05-11T07:05:41.6842495Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6843656Z 22    <!--
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6844326Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6845176Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6846030Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6847020Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6847975Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6849085Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6858837Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6859827Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6860768Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6861662Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6862395Z 33    -->
2026-05-11T07:05:41.6863363Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
